import React from 'react'
import { Container, Logo, Nav, NavLink, Name, Function } from './HeaderElements';

const Header = () => {

    return (
        <Container>
            <Logo>
                <Name>Julian van Beek</Name>
                <Function>Web Designer</Function>
            </Logo>
            <Nav>
                <NavLink to='/'>
                    Home
                </NavLink>
                <NavLink to='/portfolio'>
                    Portfolio
                </NavLink>
                <NavLink to='/about'>
                    About
                </NavLink>
                <NavLink to='/contact'>
                    Contact
                </NavLink>
            </Nav>
        </Container>
    );
}

export default Header;
